{"tid":1531600,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[廣傳]一招密技破解三大電話難題（iPhone版）","createTime":"2019-09-02T09:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T14:54:13.000Z","uid":229801,"like":109,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"1247e17cdf32f844768d80940df0ad9596c24917","tid":1531600,"uid":229801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:26:09.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong>三大難提：</strong></ins><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 唔解鎖，但Face ID太快，點樣暫停</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">一用兩秒組合按鍵，就一定要入密碼</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 唔解鎖，但又唔記得支援熱線</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">唔駛解鎖都可以打到幾個預先設定好嘅支援熱線</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 唔解鎖，但又點證明部電話係你嘅</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">唔解鎖都可以講得出預先設定好嘅家人電話</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">答案：就係用iPhone嘅 緊急求助SOS 同埋 醫療檔案內嘅緊急聯絡人！</span></span></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多，跟圖自學！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/487ivBC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F487ivBC.png&h=202a254d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NsMLaBD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNsMLaBD.png&h=b437bb13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R9pT3WE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR9pT3WE.png&h=760da26e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>跟據以上步驟設定好 緊急求助SOS 嘅 聯絡人<br />\n<br />\n就可以跟以下步驟咁樣發動密技</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HuWnXip.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHuWnXip.png&h=410af4f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只要保持按鍵約兩秒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lx32cRL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLx32cRL.png&h=a86f62fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A3mWhiq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA3mWhiq.png&h=fb546c94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有兄弟設定途中要入個人資料，其實係「健康」依個app入面嘅個人檔案，亂入都得。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZA0JZi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZA0JZi.png&h=2e37f904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>溫馨提示：一定要測試！！實戰時未開波就要發動啦！唔好諗住訓咗落地先發動！<br />\n同埋親友聯絡人要搵醒目信得過又一定會安坐家中果啲吖！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>今日新疆 明日香港<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n手兄爬山 各自努力<br />\n香港人 加油！</strong></span></span></em>"},{"pid":"c2cd80790027f07e6ed5357694dfcebb0c024ff1","tid":1531600,"uid":287449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借位宣傳<br />\n侵侵同d外國人都冇加你fb同ig，點知你想要咩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好再係facebook同ig自己圍爐打飛機啦，一齊黎開始國際戰線！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個tweet幾秒鐘，一蚊都唔洗，又唔洗綁電話，安全又快捷，快d一齊轉用twitter啦<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">twitter文宣共識TG</span>： </span></strong><a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR2z%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=1fedd181\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n內有twitter詳細教學，開個account唔洗3分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文唔好驚比人笑？唔洗驚，國際文宣谷幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n🔥<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>反送中 國際文宣谷link</strong></span></span>🔥<br />\n